name: Lucky Shot (V)
Lore: 'AT-ATs are nearly impervious to infantry fire, but occasionally a blaster bolt hits between the plating. It''s one shot in a million, but such odds are a familiar to the Rebellion.',
Text: 'If opponent''s Effect of any kind was just lost or canceled due to its own game text, place it out of play. OR Until end of turn, Do They Have A Code Clearance? may not modify forfeit. OR Cancel Close Call. OR Cancel Outflank (you may activate 1 Force).',
